OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FMore than two hundred pupils at a
OL,7,Fsecondary school have been suspended
OL,8,Fin around three weeks after tough new
OL,9,Fdisciplinary procedures were brought
OL,10,Fin.
OL,12,FSt Edmund Arrowsmith Catholic Academy
OL,13,Fin Whiston, Merseyside said the
OL,14,Fmeasures aim to 'raise the bar' of
OL,15,Fwhat is expected - but some parents
OL,16,Fhave called the actions 'extreme' and
OL,17,Fsay they are leaving children anxious
OL,18,Fabout going to school.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
