OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FThe academy made headlines in summer
OL,7,F2024 after the school's headteacher
OL,8,FLee Peachey and deputy head Anna Kenny
OL,9,Fwere suddenly absent from their roles
OL,10,Fwithout explanation.
OL,12,FMore than a year later both senior
OL,13,Ffigures remain away from the school,
OL,14,Falthough both remain listed on the
OL,15,Fschool's website. Clare McKenna is the
OL,16,Fcurrent acting headteacher.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
