OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FThe mysterious absences - which have
OL,7,Fstill not been explained to parents by
OL,8,Fthe Pope Francis Catholic Multi-
OL,9,FAcademy Trust that runs the school -
OL,10,Fcame after a moment of celebration for
OL,11,FSt Edmund Arrowsmith, which in May
OL,12,F2024 saw its Ofsted rating moved out
OL,13,Fof inadequate for the first time since
OL,14,F2015.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
