OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FBut in recent weeks, school bosses
OL,7,Fhave decided that if they are to move
OL,8,Fthe school beyond its current
OL,9,F'requires improvement' rating, then
OL,10,Fmajor changes are needed to tackle
OL,11,Fsome behaviour issues amongst its
OL,12,Fpupils.
OL,14,FThe school has been working with the
OL,15,FEducation Exchange - a network of
OL,16,Fschools, local authorities and
OL,17,Feducation providers that offers
OL,18,Fguidance to schools - on its new
OL,19,Fdisciplinary policies, which have
OL,20,Fresulted in scores of suspensions and
OL,21,Fexclusions of pupils.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
