OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FIn the first week of the new policy
OL,7,Fcoming in a total of 99 suspensions
OL,8,Fwere handed out at the school,
OL,9,Faccording to local paper, the
OL,10,FLiverpool Echo.
OL,12,FWeek two saw 67 suspensions, while
OL,13,Fweek three saw 36. The school believes
OL,14,Fthis downward trajectory as a sign
OL,15,Fthat students are understanding what
OL,16,Fis now expected of them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
