OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FMany of these suspensions resulted in
OL,7,Fpupils being sent home for the day.
OL,8,FThe school says this would only happen
OL,9,Fafter a pupil had repeatedly refused
OL,10,Fto follow a reasonable demand from
OL,11,Fstaff.
OL,13,FBut the new approach has come under
OL,14,Ffire by some parents. One dad, who
OL,15,Fasked not to be named because his
OL,16,Fchild is a pupil at the school, said
OL,17,Fthe measures were 'extreme' and
OL,18,Fresulting in large numbers of kids
OL,19,Fmissing school for minor issues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
