OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FHe said: "I am finding the reasonings
OL,7,Ffor the punishments to be minor and,
OL,8,Fin my opinion, not befitting of a day
OL,9,Fin isolation and/or suspension.
OL,11,F"In my opinion the school is not
OL,12,Ftackling the root cause and are not
OL,13,Fconsidering reasons for children or
OL,14,Ftheir behaviours on individual merit,
OL,15,Fit appears to be a new blanket policy
OL,16,Fand dishing out punishments."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
