OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FHe claimed many children have now
OL,7,Fbecome "anxious and worried about
OL,8,Fgoing to school", also claiming that
OL,9,Fthe school is not properly
OL,10,Fcommunicating issues with parents or
OL,11,Fgiving enough notice of isolations and
OL,12,Fsuspensions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
