OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FHe said: "It literally has become a
OL,7,Fguessing game, and it will be
OL,8,Faffecting many parents and their work
OL,9,Fgiven that we never know if we need to
OL,10,Fpick our child up early, if they are
OL,11,Fin class or not, or if they are in
OL,12,Fisolation or have a one-hour
OL,13,Fdetention, which is the normal
OL,14,Fprocedure."
