OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,FIn a statement regarding the school's
OL,7,Fnew procedures, acting head Clare
OL,8,FMcKenna said: "Since our recent Ofsted
OL,9,Finspection was published just over a
OL,10,Fyear ago, which was the school's first
OL,11,Fmore positive outcome in more than a
OL,12,Fdecade, we have achieved a great deal,
OL,13,Fand progress has been made.
OL,15,F"The support we have received from
OL,16,Fmany has been hugely appreciated. We
OL,17,Falso recognise, however, that there
OL,18,Fwere elements of the school which were
OL,19,Fholding back further improvements `
OL,20,Fparticularly in relation to behaviour
OL,21,Fand expectations.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
