OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,F"We spent a great deal of time looking
OL,7,Fat how best we could overcome these
OL,8,Fhurdles. In response, we have utilised
OL,9,Four involvement with the Education
OL,10,FExchange, a professional group of
OL,11,Fleading educationalists who share best
OL,12,Fpractice, expertise and experience, to
OL,13,Fhelp us develop some additional
OL,14,Ftargeted approaches.
OL,16,F"This has resulted in us raising the
OL,17,Fbar in terms of what we expect of all
OL,18,Four pupils.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
