OL,3,CMore than 200 pupils suspended from
OL,4,Csecondary school in three weeks
OL,6,F"There has been some push back from
OL,7,Fparents, but this has been
OL,8,Fsignificantly outweighed by the number
OL,9,Fof positive comments we have received.
OL,10,FThat is why we have held coffee
OL,11,Fmornings and invited people in to see
OL,12,Fthe new expectations in action ` the
OL,13,Fchange is tangible and having a very
OL,14,Fpositive impact.
OL,16,F"Ultimately, we all want the very best
OL,17,Ffor our brilliant pupils. Behaviour is
OL,18,Fimproving, children are happier and
OL,19,Flearning is more focused."
